(52675, 155509, 4851, 13, '美好夢', '', '2012-08-15 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 2, '', '當我和你在走\n就像在美好夢裡\n聽到你最感動\n唱歌在我的耳裡\n你給我一種自然嗨\n像我能飛 and touch the sky\n也沒有什麼不明白\n全世界上最美的愛, 愛\n\n\n進到我的美好夢\n放上我的 favorite song\n感受它的愛\n讓你回不來\nFly away, oh, butterfly [butterfly]\n\n\n像個 butterfly\n沒跟著你覺得 superfly\nLike I, I, I could touch the sky\n碰到那個雲, 飛的那麼嗨\n像個太空人或著風箏\n跟著風吹, sway like I''m floatin''\n就在海邊 chillin'' by the ocean\n這種環境聽不到 no bullshit\nSo I fly away\n像是蝴蝶 on a summer day\n有的時候這個社會, 會\n讓你瘋, wanna run away\n對, to another place\nSomewhere where it''s safe\nMaybe far away\n但是不管那裡去\n只要有你, 水\n\nWhen I''m with you it''s like:\na fairy tale beginning, a story never ending baby\nWhen I''m with you it''s like:\na beautiful enchantment like Jasmine and Aladdin baby\nWhen I''m with you it''s like:\nI''m sitting on a cloud with butterflies around me baby\nWhen I''m with you it''s like:\nI''m floating in the sky, or on a natural high', 260, '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-08-13 16:25:46', '2015-03-12 13:55:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
