(52681, 6216, 4809, 3, 'The end of the world', '', '2012-08-03 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 16, 'Why does the sun go on shining? \r\n陽光怎能繼續閃耀\r\nWhy does the sea rush to shore? \r\n浪花何以持續淘沖海灘\r\nDon''t they know it''s the end of the world? \r\n難道他們不見末日到來\r\n''Cause you don''t love me anymore \r\n因你對我的愛早已不再\r\n\r\n\r\nWhy do the birds go on singing? \r\n飛鳥怎能繼續歌唱\r\nWhy do the stars glow above? \r\n星辰何以持續閃爍穹蒼\r\nDon''t they know it''s the end of the world? \r\n難道他們不見末日到來\r\nIt ended when I lost your love \r\n我失去你的愛末日便已存在\r\n\r\n\r\nI wake up in the morning \r\n清晨醒來\r\nAnd I wonder why everything''s the same as it was \r\n我懷疑萬物何以還能運作依舊\r\nI can''t understand, no I can''t understand \r\n我不懂，真的不懂\r\nHow life goes on the way it does \r\n生命怎能一如往常地流動\r\n\r\n\r\nWhy does my heart go on beating? \r\n我的心居然仍在跳動\r\nWhy do these eyes of mine cry? \r\n我的眼如何卻還哭泣\r\nDon''t they know it''s the end of the world? \r\n難道他們不見末日到來\r\nIt ended when I lost your love \r\n我失去你的愛末日便已存在\r\n\r\n\r\nDon''t they know it''s the end of the world? \r\n難道他們不見末日到來\r\nIt ended when you said goodbye\r\n你與我道別末日便已存在\r\n', '', 150, '家家', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-08-13 17:40:11', '2015-03-12 13:55:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(52682, 6216, 4809, 5, 'Homecoming fool', '', '2012-08-03 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 16, 'I left my hometown to search for gold\r\n我離家去淘金			 \r\nI told my sweetheart soon I''ll be home\r\n告訴愛人我會很快返來	\r\n		\r\nTo seal our love with a diamond ring\r\n帶一只鑽戒封訂我倆的真情\r\nShe''ll be my queen and I''ll be her king\r\n屆時，她做我女王，我做她天帝	\r\n			\r\nBut when I reached the promised land\r\n可我到了傳言中的應許之地  \r\nAll I found was heaps of sand\r\n放眼望去盡是成堆無用的砂粒	\r\nSo my love left me for someone new\r\n愛人於是拋下我去尋就新的戀情	\r\nAnd now they hail me homecoming fool\r\n如今人人管我叫落魄還鄉的傻子哩\r\n', '', 87, 'Soler', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-08-13 17:43:07', '2015-03-12 13:55:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
