(52702, 6216, 4809, 8, 'On the other side', '', '2012-08-03 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 16, 'On the other side\r\n換個情境\r\nThe grass is greener on the other side\r\n草地更綠\r\nThey always end up feeling satisfied\r\n萬事終歸落得盡如人意\r\nOh on the other side\r\n喔，只要換個情境\r\n\r\n\r\nOn the other side\r\n換個情境\r\nNow will I meet you on the other side\r\n好不好我們現在就換個情境相見\r\nI hope it won''t be all brimstone and fire\r\n但願彼方並不滿佈硫石燄火\r\nThere on the other side\r\n在那全新的境界\r\n\r\n\r\nOn the other side\r\n切入你的情境\r\nYou tend to come across as self-assured \r\n你老顯得如此充滿自信\r\nBut really I don''t think you''re all that pure\r\n但老實說，我也不覺你有那麼純粹淨美\r\nThere on the other side\r\n即便在你的境地\r\n\r\n\r\nOn the other side\r\n進入你的情境\r\nDo you ever look beyond your shores\r\n你是否曾經跨越侷限\r\nRight across from you or down the hall\r\n真切看進另一個世界，看悠長廊道的深處\r\nOh on the other side\r\n進入新的境界\r\n\r\n\r\nMeet you on the other side\r\n到新的境地見\r\nSee you on the other side\r\n不如我們換個情境相見\r\n', '', 73, 'Soler', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-08-14 15:14:56', '2015-03-12 13:55:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(52703, 6216, 4809, 9, 'Raindrops', '', '2012-08-03 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 16, 'From the start there was nothing but air\r\n太初原始，萬事俱空，唯有虛氣\r\nonly moisture on your skin and hair\r\n唯有你膚髮上的溼氣			    \r\nWe were moon\r\n你我是月			   \r\nWe were stars\r\n是星\r\nWe were sand\r\n是沙塵				 \r\nNow we''re children of a long lost land\r\n而今，我們成了失落樂園的遺族\r\n			\r\nAnd we all fall down\r\n皆盡沉落			   \r\nYeah we all fall down\r\n是的，你我皆盡沉落\r\nOh we all fall down like raindrops we fall down\r\n喔，沉落，一如雨點，我們盡數沉落\r\n', '', 93, 'Soler', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-08-14 15:18:09', '2015-03-12 13:55:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(52704, 6216, 4809, 10, 'Railroad Dream', '', '2012-08-03 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 16, 'I crossed the northern hemisphere\r\n跨越北半球\r\nDowned a pint or two o'' beer\r\n乾掉一、兩杯啤酒\r\nI''m thinking\r\n我想\r\nI''m sinking\r\n我是在向下沉落\r\n\r\nI jumped train like Steve Mcqueen\r\n學史蒂夫.馬昆＊那樣跳火車\r\nI''m the hero of my dreams\r\n我是我夢裡的大英雄\r\nI''m dreamin''\r\n我夢見\r\nI''m steamin''\r\n我在急速移動\r\n\r\nThere''s a railroad running through\r\n一路鐵道穿越\r\nThere''s a railroad running through\r\n一路鐵道穿越\r\nThere''s a railroad, honey, \r\n寶貝，有路鐵道\r\nRunning right through me\r\n不偏不移穿越					 \r\n\r\nRunning right through me\r\n不偏不移穿越我\r\n\r\nI''m dreamin''\r\n我在做夢\r\nBig time dreaming\r\n超級大夢\r\n                     \r\nThere''s a railroad honey\r\n有路鐵道，寶貝\r\nRunning right through me\r\n不偏不移穿越				\r\n\r\nRunning right through me...\r\n不偏不移穿越我\r\n\r\n＊史蒂夫.馬昆（Steve McQueen）是一九六、七〇年代的好萊塢動作片明星。此句典故出自馬昆在一九六三年出品的The Great Escape一片中，跳火車逃亡的片段。\r\n', '', 80, 'Soler', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-08-14 15:20:12', '2015-03-12 13:55:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
