(52707, 6216, 4809, 13, 'All the young dudes', '', '2012-08-03 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 16, '\r\nWell Billy rapped all night about his suicide\r\nBilly念了一整夜要去自殺\r\nHow he kick it in the head when he was twenty-five\r\n可是他才二十五歲怎麼腦子裡裝這些東西\r\nSpeed jive don''t want to stay alive\r\n看你飆車的速度根本不想活了\r\nWhen you''re twenty-five\r\n但你才二十五歲\r\n\r\nAnd Wendy''s stealing clothes from Marks and Sparks\r\nWendy在賣場偷衣服\r\nAnd Freedy''s got spots from ripping off the stars from his face funky little boat race\r\nFreedy在划船比賽打架卻贏來更多眼光\r\n\r\nTelevision man is crazy saying were juvenile deliquent wrecks\r\n電視上的人瘋著議論青少年犯罪\r\nOh man I need TV when I got T-Rex\r\n拜託誰轉個台我要看恐龍雷克斯\r\nOh brother you guessed\r\n兄弟你猜對了\r\nI''m a dude dad\r\n我把她肚子搞大了\r\n\r\nAll the young dudes\r\n但所有的年輕人\r\nCarry the news\r\n誰能不撐起這個時代\r\nBoogaloo dudes\r\n舞步嘻哈的年輕人\r\nCarry the news\r\n我們肩負一個新時代\r\n\r\nAll the young dudes\r\n所有的年輕人\r\nCarry the news\r\n我們肩負這個時代\r\nBoogaloo dudes\r\n舞步嘻哈的年輕人\r\nCarry the news\r\n承擔新的時代\r\n\r\nNow lucy looks sweet cause he dresses like a queen\r\n看lucy扮妝得像個女王多可愛\r\nBut he can kick like a mule its a real mean team\r\n但是他踢人的時候就像騾子一樣凶\r\nBut we can love oh yes we can love\r\n但是我們還能愛 對 我們還能愛\r\n\r\nAnd my brothers back at home with his Beatles and his Stones\r\n我的兄弟帶著披頭四和滾石的唱片回家\r\nWe never got it off on that revolution stuff\r\n我們永遠喊著革命萬歲\r\nWhat a drag   Too many snags\r\n但到底誰又改變什麼\r\n\r\nNow I''ve drunk a lot of wine and I''m feeling fine\r\n反正我喝了很多 感覺還不賴\r\nGot to race some cats to bed\r\n去泡妞吧\r\nOh is there concrete all around\r\n反正到處是冷硬的牆\r\nOr is it in my head\r\n或者這通通是我的幻想\r\nOh brother you guessed\r\n兄弟你答對了\r\nI''m a dude dad\r\n我剛當上爸爸\r\n\r\nAll the young dudes\r\n所有的你們\r\nCarry the news\r\n肩膀上有了新時代\r\nBoogaloo dudes\r\n舞步嘻哈的年輕人\r\nCarry the news\r\n擔起一個新時代\r\n\r\n', '', 219, 'Sammy So', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-08-14 15:32:15', '2015-03-12 13:55:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
